title: Various Artists - Slow Motion (Ambient/Chillout Compilation)
description:
A start with finest motion.

The first release in 2008 is a colourful and trippy chill out and lounge collection with magical and unique ambient tunes.

Some known artists of Blue Tunes show us another side with fresh and hypnotic atmospheres.

This journey will be one-of-a-kind and overwhelming with warm and soft beats.


Label: Blue Tunes Recordings
Year: 2008/ 06 week
Total time approx.: 66 mins.
Format: mp3/192
